Collections.rule:
Individual: @A*
Types: StorageUnit
Facts:	providedBy @B*,
	hasState @C*,
	hasType @D*

Individual: @A*
Types: ComputeUnit
Facts:	providedBy @B*,
	hasState @C*

Individual: @A*
Types: Federation
Facts: 	hasAccountingName @B*,
	hasTier @C*(mm:prepend("Tier")),
	hasCountry @E*

Individual: @A*
Types: Service
Facts:	hasType @B*,
	hasFlavour @C*,
	providedBy @D*,
	hasState @E*

Individual: @A*
Types: RCSite
Facts:	hasCountry @B*,
	hasFederation @C*,
	hasTier @D*(mm:prepend("Tier")),
	hasStatus @E*,
	hasState @F*

Individual: @A*
Types: DDMEndpoint
Facts:	providedBy @B*,
	hasType @E*,
	hasState @G*,
	usedBy @H*(["^(.+?)@"])

Individual: @A*
Types: CMSSite
Facts:	hasState @B*,
	hasCountry @C*,
	hasFacility @D*,
	hasStatus @E*,
	hasTier @F*(mm:prepend("Tier"))

Individual: @A*
Types: ExperimentSite
Facts: 	hasState @C*,
	hasTier @F*(mm:prepend("Tier")),
	hasStatus @G*,
	hasCountry @D*,
	hasVOName @E*
